4:41.000Z","msg":"政治逼害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7b831c8e79e35bf68826072af9cf6261e5a6a6","tid":678372,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:20:05.000Z","msg":"呢 D 咪就係對人唔對事"}]}